title: Summoner icons missing
body:
Dear Support

I haven't received these events' rewarding icons since March of 2017, which include the 'Advanced Bot tests LIVE in Normals' and the 'Dark Star 2017'. My alternative account has received both icons in the same PC with the same client already. 

I was trying to submit a ticket but the support web page keeps redirecting me to the board, so please help me to fix this and give what these events promised these summoner icons. Thank you so much.

Regards
